values.summary:
Engineer Java applications and RESTful Web services for aiding researchers in different studies of epidemic diseases
• Develop Web service framework to retrieve bioinformatics datasets using structural metadata supporting either relational or NoSQL databases as the backend
• Improve response time by executing optimized SELECT statements created from Hibernate connection
• Use Hibernate to extract data from Oracle and then transform and load into a different schema in MySQL
• Employ ElasticSearch (a distributed NoSQL database and index) to support real­time retrieval of medications sales data for a biosurveillance system
• Design and maintain database different schemas for different projects driven by their constraints
• Maintain Spring applications containing NLP plugins
• Re-architect a Java application to be a Grails application as RESTful Web services
• Educate team to dynamic programming as an alternative solution to a programming problem
• Re­architect and convert a Java application to use Grails and RESTful Web services
• Also use: Eclipse, JUnit, JSON, XML, Groovy, Maven, Ant, Ivy, Jersey, YourKit, Tomcat, SVN, JavaScript, jQuery, JIRA, HTML
